further research prefix:
During the analysis of summaries obtained by different methods, we identified several features:
    ‚Ä¢ mBART has the lowest level of abstractiveness compared to ruGPT3Large and ruT5-large;
    ‚Ä¢ ruGPT3Small and ruGPT3Large generate summaries that are closest in length to the reference

         ones, but often does not complete them and makes errors;
    ‚Ä¢ ruT5-base and ruT5-large summaries are also close to the reference length, rather abstract and

         contain fewer errors than summaries of ruGPT3Small and ruGPT3Large;
    ‚Ä¢ TextRank more evenly selects sentences from the text;
    ‚Ä¢ LexRank tends to select sentences from the beginning of the text.

